                                                            "text": "\ud83c\udf8a\ud83d\udfe02nd Annual Orange Me Contest \ud83c\udf8a\ud83d\udfe0  \n\n\u23f0Starts today ends March 3, 2025 11:59 PM Eastern, New York Time   \n\nTotal to be collected:  \n\n\ud83d\udd35ETH (no base) 0.5 Foundation, OS, Major platforms \n\ud83d\udfe0SOL / Solana 5.0 1/1\u2019s only \n\ud83d\udd34XTZ / Objkt 500 XTZ  \n\n\ud83d\udea8All set to buy now or make offer, no auctions.  \n\n\ud83c\udf8aInvite friends to join \nRepost/like  \n\n\ud83d\udea8Include when dropping art: \nHashtag: #ORANGEME2025 \nBlockchain, Art Image and link  \n\nAny style all art welcome, orange color preferred \ud83d\udfe0  \n\nAny questions when I am not active direct to \nKosar @kosaramiri_eth  \n\nLet\u2019s have some fun! \nLet\u2019s create some beautiful art!!!! \nGood luck to everyone!!!",
